reviews.review_text: This is my favorite BK. Staff are friendly, helpful and doing their best to keep area and tables clean. Dining is large enough with plenty sitting tables and stools. Free parking lot in front. Food quality is good and free refill for drinks available. BK has always good offers if install the App or use coupons. Save your time and money  with order ahead by mobile app is the best choice.
I had my lunch in this location today. I had a good experience. Alex was a nice young man friendly and without attitude who helped me with my order. I will definitely come back.

We were very happy with our order,s keep up the good work everyone. And there resturaunt is always clean. also the customers social distance, there is markers on the floors . The best fast food restaurant i have been to. The classic whopper meal with chicken fries and a medium mango juice. The chicken fries was extremely smooth. You can taste the chicken melted in the cheese. And a barbecue dipping sauce made my experience spectacular. Just as i enjoyed my moment with one chicken fries as starters i very amused. The classic whopper sandwich contained with fresh vegetables, salty pickle and the fresh juicy taste of tomato. The classic whopper sandwich with processed cheddar cheese and the ounce of pure beef meat. The melted cheese in the meat combined with mayo ketchup and mustered. The classic whopper burger was the best burger i have ever had in my entire life.
